      "text": "## 🗺️ Regional Civilization Map\n\n**Fertile Crescent & Beyond**\n\n**Oldest Civilizations by Region:**\n\n**1. Anatolia/ Turkey**
- Göbekli Tepe (~9500 BCE)\n- Çatalhöyük (~7500 BCE)\n\n**2. Mesopotamia**
- Sumerian cities (~5500 BCE)\n- Babylon, Ur, Uruk\n\n**3. Nile Valley**
- Ancient Egypt (~5500 BCE)\n- Memphis, pyramids\n\n**4. Indus Basin**
- Harappa, Mohenjo-Daro (~3300 BCE)\n\n**5. Andes**
- Caral-Supe (~3100 BCE)",
      "x": -200,
