      "type": "text",
      "text": "🔗 Ancient Trade Routes\n\n**Major Pathways:**\n\n**Royal Road**\n- Persia: 2,700 km\n- Connected cities\n\n**Silk Road** (later)\n- China ↔ Rome\n- 6,400 km network\n\n**Indian Ocean Trade**\n- Mesopotamia ↔ Indus\n- Maritime routes\n\n**Materials Traded:**\n- Obsidian, flint, copper\n- Textiles, ceramics\n- Spices, precious stones",
